# NOTE: src/nanopdf.js and src/nanopdf.wasm (the prebuilt Emscripten module) are
# committed on purpose so the GitHub Pages deploy can build the viewer without an
# Emscripten toolchain. Rebuild + recommit them when the C++ changes
# (see scripts/bootstrap-emscripten.sh).

